---
title: Chicken Sausage & Sweet Potato Soup Easy Cleanup
description: As the temperature continues to drop, we find ourselves craving the culinary equivalent of a cozy blanket. Enter this hearty, soul-warming soup. It’s chock full of goodness — that is to say spiced chicken sausage, chunks of sweet potato, and tender curly kale. And because no good brothy bowl is complete without some bread for dunking, we’re also throwing in buttery, herby toast points. Get ready for a meal as satisfying as it is delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e6900abce29b57e475f66b0-845224d4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-sausage-sweet-potato-soup-5e6900abce29b57e475f66b0-af554ce1.pdf
